author: rhuijben
msg: Upgrade working copy format to format 18 to switch to in-db properties.
Another step on the way to the full WC-NG layout. Switching this will make
your WC-NG workingcopy import the property files on upgrade and then delete
Keeping the properties out of the database is slowing down wc-ng development,
as the fourth tree and single-db require in-db properties and several code
cleanups can't be performed because all property operations were still
performed twice: once on the db and once on the files (via a wq operation).
